          {
            "title": "Replace",
            "id": 82603,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos substituir uma parte de uma string armazenada dentro de uma variável primeiro codificando o nome da variável e a instrução <code>replace()</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"special = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Today's special is pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"new_special = special.replace()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"60\" endIndex=\"67\" /><option startIndex=\"67\" endIndex=\"68\" /><option startIndex=\"68\" endIndex=\"69\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>replace</code> seguido de <code>(</code> e finalmente <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Values",
            "id": 82604,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Dentro dos parênteses, adicionamos a parte que queremos substituir, como <code>\"pasta\"</code>, uma vírgula, e então o novo valor, <code>\"pizza\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"special = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Today's special is pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"new_special = special.replace(\" /><text value=\"&quot;pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\",\" /><text value=\"&quot;pizza&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"68\" endIndex=\"75\" /><option startIndex=\"75\" endIndex=\"76\" /><option startIndex=\"76\" endIndex=\"83\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"pasta\"</code> seguido de <code>,</code> e finalmente <code>\"pizza\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Displaying",
