            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Ao codificar <code>print(new_special)</code>, podemos ver que a variável <code>new_special</code> contém a string atualizada.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"special = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Today's special is pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"new_special = special.replace(\" /><text value=\"&quot;pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\",\" /><text value=\"&quot;pizza&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(new_special)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"86\" endIndex=\"91\" /><option startIndex=\"91\" endIndex=\"92\" /><option startIndex=\"92\" endIndex=\"103\" /><option startIndex=\"103\" endIndex=\"104\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Today's special is pizza\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>print</code> seguido de <code>(</code> e depois <code>new_special</code>, <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
